{
  "id": "postcard-travel",
  "name": "旅行明信片",
  "category": "postcard",
  "description": "一张旅行风格的明信片，带有风景照片和旅行元素",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.03,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "旅行|度假|风景|城市|海边|山川",
        "description": "旅行场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "location": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "地点"
    },
    "sender": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "发送者"
    },
    "recipient": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "接收者"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "日期"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 300,
      "description": "明信片内容"
    },
    "weather": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "晴朗",
      "options": ["晴朗", "多云", "雨天", "雪天"],
      "description": "天气"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一张旅行明信片的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 发送者：{{sender}}\n- 接收者：{{recipient}}\n- 地点：{{location}}\n- 天气：{{weather}}\n\n要求：\n1. 使用轻松愉快的旅行语言\n2. 内容要带有对风景的描述和感受\n3. 语气要温馨亲切\n4. 字数控制在100-200字之间\n\n请直接输出明信片内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "postcard",
    "colors": ["#f5f5f5", "#87ceeb", "#ffd700"],
    "mood": "轻松愉快"
  },
  "rarity": "uncommon",
  "collectible": true
}